      "topic": "life",
      "content": "Life is the condition that distinguishes organisms from inorganic matter, characterized by growth, reproduction, adaptation, and response to stimuli. Philosophically, life raises questions about meaning, purpose, and consciousness. Biologically, life emerged on Earth about 3.8 billion years ago and has evolved into incredible diversity.",
